href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a> 				</div> 				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Book_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Book (disambiguation)">Book (disambiguation)</a>.</div> <div class="thumb tright"> <div class="thumbinner" style="width:312px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Book_Collage.png" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3d/Book_Collage.png/310px-Book_Collage.png" width="310" height="202" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3d/Book_Collage.png/465px-Book_Collage.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3d/Book_Collage.png/620px-Book_Collage.png 2x" data-file-width="3471" data-file-height="2258" /></a> <div class="thumbcaption"> <div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Book_Collage.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div> Books</div> </div> </div> <table class="vertical-navbox nowraplinks" style="float:right;clear:right;width:22.0em;margin:0 0 1.0em 1.0em;background:#f9f9f9;border:1px solid #aaa;padding:0.2em;border-spacing:0.4em 0;text-align:center;line-height:1.4em;font-size:88%"> <tr> <th style="padding:0.2em 0.4em 0.2em;font-size:145%;line-height:1.2em;padding-bottom:0"><a href="/wiki/Literature" title="Literature">Literature</a></th> </tr> <tr> <td style="padding:0.2em 0 0.4em"><a href="/wiki/File:Liji2.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Liji2.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0c/Liji2.jpg/175px-Liji2.jpg" width="175" height="105" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0c/Liji2.jpg/263px-Liji2.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0c/Liji2.jpg/350px-Liji2.jpg 2x" data-file-width="1945" data-file-height="1172" /></a></td> </tr> <tr> <th class="navbox-abovebelow" style="padding:0.1em">Major forms</